        "type": "equation",
        "title": "z / t CI for mean",
        "latex": "\\bar{x}\\pm z^{*}\\frac{\\sigma}{\\sqrt{n}}\\quad\\text{or}\\quad\\bar{x}\\pm t^{*}_{n-1}\\frac{s}{\\sqrt{n}}"
